{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"de117b86fe","title":"对中南海门诊部关于周恩来心脏病情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2dff12ca9d","index":0,"year":1972,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"de117b86fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"dce20b5b08","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中南海门诊部下志强、张佐良1972年11月11日给叶剑英等中央领导人写报告说，昨晚再次组织了有关的心脏科医生会诊，大家一致认为：恩来同志的心脏病发展是比较重的，动脉硬化的情况，特别是主动脉硬化引起主动脉膜关闭不全的情况有所加重，导致冠状动脉供血不足及心脏功能均较前为差，要及时严重注意。平时虽随时研究病情，调整治疗，但药物的力量毕竟有限，宜特别注意休息，增加睡眠，采取减轻工作和其他一些可行的办法。希望中央领导同志考虑，并给以指示。毛泽东着到报告后写了这个批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3dacc9f2b8","type":"title","text":"对中南海门诊部关于周恩来心脏病情况报告的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe"},{"id":"dce20b5b08","type":"paragraph","text":"应当休息、节劳。不可大意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe"},{"id":"24c0480a1b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe"},{"id":"61f986f373","type":"paragraph","text":"1972,11，12","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe"}],"page":{"id":"14710222df","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"de117b86fe","start":360,"end":360}}}},"__N_SSG":true}